{"tid":1763090,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"大學校園開放任人出入 楊潤雄促檢討改善","createTime":"2019-11-30T05:12:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-30T05:21:04.000Z","uid":10540,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"b006ccb12ac7c6d485448fd20b335912e607c642","tid":1763090,"uid":10540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-30T05:12:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/RY_bSKCwO0Eihj8WnqV2pA--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9ODAwO2lsPXBsYW5l/http://media.zenfs.com/en_us/News/singtao/20191130a103747.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FRY_bSKCwO0Eihj8WnqV2pA--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9ODAwO2lsPXBsYW5l%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fen_us%2FNews%2Fsingtao%2F20191130a103747.jpg&h=26ac1812&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【星島日報報道】警方昨日解封理工大學，將校園交回校方管理。教育局局長楊潤雄表示，事件中沒有發生嚴重受傷事故，形容是令人較安心的結局。他又認為，經過今次事件，香港的大學未來應該要檢討及改善日常管理、運作等，一但再發生類似情況，會如何應對。<br />\n<br />\n楊潤雄出席一個電台節目時表示，警方有責任維持治安，保障市民生命及財產安全，強調警方在今次在事件中保持克制，並盡最大努力，期望留守者自願走出來。他又重申，解決現時的困局不一定要訴諸暴力，期望理大能夠回復正常運作。<br />\n<br />\n楊潤雄又說，今次事件影響了整個專上界別，除了在硬件上有損失外，學校提早結束學期，亦令大專生的學習受影響，部分外地生及內地生更因為擔心人身安全，決定離開香港。當局會主動聯絡各間大學，並提供協助。<br />\n<br />\n他又指，各大學未來應該檢討及改善日常管理、運作等，又舉例指不少校園及宿舍都開放予所有人，從安全考慮上是否應作檢討，考慮如何做到平衡。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E4%BF%AE%E4%BE%8B%E9%A2%A8%E6%B3%A2-%E5%A4%A7%E5%AD%B8%E6%A0%A1%E5%9C%92%E9%96%8B%E6%94%BE%E4%BB%BB%E4%BA%BA%E5%87%BA%E5%85%A5-%E6%A5%8A%E6%BD%A4%E9%9B%84%E4%BF%83%E6%AA%A2%E8%A8%8E%E6%94%B9%E5%96%84-021000390.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E4%25BF%25AE%25E4%25BE%258B%25E9%25A2%25A8%25E6%25B3%25A2-%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E5%25AD%25B8%25E6%25A0%25A1%25E5%259C%2592%25E9%2596%258B%25E6%2594%25BE%25E4%25BB%25BB%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E5%2587%25BA%25E5%2585%25A5-%25E6%25A5%258A%25E6%25BD%25A4%25E9%259B%2584%25E4%25BF%2583%25E6%25AA%25A2%25E8%25A8%258E%25E6%2594%25B9%25E5%2596%2584-021000390.html&d=ZahK9au6JYDyKCuDEpipf3yU4AarvyINc8S1qmu5ZLM%3D&h=c8589240\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E4%BF%AE%E4%BE%8B%E9%A2%A8%E6%B3%A2-%E5%A4%A7%E5%AD%B8%E6%A0%A1%E5%9C%92%E9%96%8B%E6%94%BE%E4%BB%BB%E4%BA%BA%E5%87%BA%E5%85%A5-%E6%A5%8A%E6%BD%A4%E9%9B%84%E4%BF%83%E6%AA%A2%E8%A8%8E%E6%94%B9%E5%96%84-021000390.html</a>"},{"pid":"ff5c63bd887661aaf28836ff114d277a157c405d","tid":1763090,"uid":114064,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-30T05:13:15.000Z","msg":"教育局管到大學嘅咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"046b9dd91fd86634c108889b88192a23ff83559d","tid":1763090,"uid":314731,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-30T05:21:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}